{"tid":862471,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻倉鼠個頰囊跌左出嚟","createTime":"2018-10-15T00:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T15:47:33.000Z","uid":62754,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c673626c4c75354a9aff49587393175a4c02219a","tid":862471,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:28:05.000Z","msg":"半夜就見到佢個嘴吊住舊粉紅色好似肉球嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚影啲相唔係太清 而家又廢事嘈醒佢<br />\n但係佢情況同下面段片一樣<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8ft7CKTg5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8ft7CKTg5w&d=o6wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=02a847cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8ft7CKTg5w</a><br />\n半夜上網睇話大圍間24小時唔好<br />\n所以就諗住今朝先帶鼠鼠出去睇<br />\n上網check過頰囊掉出一係塞返入去<br />\n一係做手術切左佢<br />\n但塞返入去都可能會成日跌返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見啲人話毛國界幾好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但會唔會好貴？<br />\n做手術大概幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n佢未有事係咁的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/082312_54618b85ce531020ef944b1d6638bce1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F082312_54618b85ce531020ef944b1d6638bce1.png&h=0c7fbbfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家右邊嘴下面有舊野吊下吊下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢暫時情況都OK 仲會食野飲水<br />\n不過佢會狂整舊野 佢應該都覺得舊野好煩好辛苦"},{"pid":"ecff2c3924fbbf94bc3b1594d87e88db285ed5cd","tid":862471,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"打針"},{"pid":"3675c12fc1597fd7cfd5ca471742c485425c5039","tid":862471,"uid":125380,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"快d睇醫生 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e714452fd401775ed215d1ce0b54895b3ceadb","tid":862471,"uid":88763,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:46:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.j-vet.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.j-vet.com&d=o6wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=46c70daa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.j-vet.com</a><br />\n<br />\n可以上去免費查詢下，隻喵之前有事都開<br />\n問過，幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d219d95dc7154e9a8f5b263c003b8adc30a07464","tid":862471,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecff2c3924fbbf94bc3b1594d87e88db285ed5cd","tid":862471,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"打針"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"打針係止痛定消腫定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee7ef1dde0d2924fccb579b35b60a6f1f63ede7","tid":862471,"uid":62754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3675c12fc1597fd7cfd5ca471742c485425c5039","tid":862471,"uid":125380,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"快d睇醫生 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係 見佢係咁狂整都知佢唔舒服"},{"pid":"0c3c042102c39d1f9b3833331a3be00517bb8dfb","tid":862471,"uid":40272,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"d219d95dc7154e9a8f5b263c003b8adc30a07464","tid":862471,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecff2c3924fbbf94bc3b1594d87e88db285ed5cd","tid":862471,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"打針"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"打針係止痛定消腫定點<img src=\"/a